Class HierarchyListUserMissionPackage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.hierarchy.HierarchyListFilter
      • com.atakmap.android.hierarchy.HierarchyListUserSelect
        • com.atakmap.android.missionpackage.ui.HierarchyListUserMissionPackage
  • public class HierarchyListUserMissionPackage
extends HierarchyListUserSelect
    Gathers all items selected by user in the Hierarchy List so they may be included in a Mission Package File Transfer. This UI is used directly by the MPT dropdown. Also see MissionPackageExportMarshal
